 \frac{a^n}{n!} = \mbox{sgn}(a)^n\frac{|a|^n}{n!} = \mbox{sgn}(a)^n\prod_{k=1}^n\frac{|a|}{ k} = \mbox{sgn}(a)^n\left(\prod_{0\leq k\leq 2a}\frac{|a|}{ k}\right)\cdot \prod_{2a< k\leq n}\frac{|a|}{ k} 
 -\left(\prod_{0\leq k\leq 2a}\frac{|a|}{ k}\right)\cdot \left( \frac{1}{2}\right)^n \leq  \mbox{sgn}(a)^n\left(\prod_{0\leq k\leq 2a}\frac{|a|}{ k}\right)\cdot \prod_{2a< k\leq n}\frac{|a|}{ k} \leq +\left(\prod_{0\leq k\leq 2a}\frac{|a|}{ k}\right)\cdot \left( \frac{1}{2}\right)^n 
v_n=\dfrac{n^a}{(1+b)^n}
\dfrac{v_{n+1}}{v_n}=\dfrac{(n+1)^a\times (1+b)^n}{(1+b)^{n+1}\times n^a}=\left(1+\dfrac{1}{n}\right)^a\times \dfrac{1}{1+b}\to\dfrac{1}{1+b}<1
e^a=\sum_{n=0}^\infty\dfrac{a^n}{n!}.
